hree\nfactorizations of the free cocompletion functor of Q-categories are presented.\nFinally, as applications, the theory of formal concept analysis and that of\nrough sets are extended to theories based on fuzzy relations between fuzzy\nsets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Aug 2014 23:58:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2015 13:08:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-15"}
